\id 2TI  
\h 2 TIMOTEO 
\toc1 2 Timoteo Umébema Carta Pauloba Timoteo Itea B̸ʌd̶a 
\toc2 2 Timoteo 
\toc3 2 Timoteo 
\mt1 2 TIMOTEO 
\mt2 UMÉBEMA CARTA PAULOBA TIMOTEO ITEA B̸ɅD̸A 
\ip Pauloba umébema carta Timoteo itea b̶ʌsid̶e wayacusa preso b̶asia. Poa 67d̶e b̶ʌsica b̶ʌa. Idji preso b̶ʌd̶ebemada ẽdrʌẽ́da crĩcha b̶ʌ bẽrã naʌ̃ cartara b̶ʌsia Timoteoba idji isabe acʌd̶e zemãrẽã (4:6-13; 4:21). 
\ip Pauloba naãrã b̶ʌsia Timoteo carea Ãcõrẽa bia b̶ʌad̶a abarida (1:1-7). Maʌ̃are b̶ʌsia Timoteora peraiẽ́ b̶ʌda Jesucrito carea ni idji preso b̶ʌ carea (1:8-18). Maʌ̃are b̶ʌsia Jesucrito ĩjã b̶ʌd̶eba zarea b̶amãrẽã idjab̶a ne jũmane Ãcõrẽ itea bia b̶amãrẽã (2:1-26). Maʌ̃are b̶ʌsia jĩrũarebema ewarid̶e minijĩchiada zeimĩna Timoteoba Ãcõrẽ bed̶eada jipa jaradia b̶aida b̶ʌda (3:1neba ab̶a 4:5d̶aa). Maʌ̃are b̶ʌsia idji cawa obʌdad̶ebemada idjab̶a jarasia Timoteora isabe zemãrẽã (4:6-22). 
\ip Dji crĩcha dromada naʌ̃gʌa: “Ãcõrẽ bed̶eara jaradia b̶adua. Ẽberãrãba ũrĩ quĩrĩã panʌne, ũrĩ quĩrĩãẽ́ panʌne bid̶a jaradiai carea b̶adua.” (2 Timoteo 4:2). 
\c 1  
\s1 Pauloba naʌ̃ cartad̶e naãrã b̶ʌd̶a 
\p  
\v 1 Mʌ̃ra Pauloa. Ãcõrẽba quĩrĩãna bẽrã mʌ̃ra Jesucritoba diabued̶aa. Idjia mʌ̃ra diabuesia Ãcõrẽba diai jarad̶a zocai b̶aid̶ebemada jarad̶e wãmãrẽã. Maʌ̃ zocai b̶aira Jesucritod̶eba b̶ʌa.  
\v 2 Timoteo, naʌ̃ cartara bʌ itea b̶ʌbʌrʌa. Mʌ̃a bʌra bio quĩrĩã b̶ʌa mʌ̃ warra quĩrãca. Quĩrĩã b̶ʌa dadji Zeza Ãcõrẽba, dadji Boro Jesucrito bid̶a bʌra quĩrã djuburia pananida, ãdji biad̶eba careba pananida, necai b̶ai sid̶a dia pananida. 
\s1 Timoteo carea Pauloba Ãcõrẽa bia b̶ʌad̶a ad̶a 
\p  
\v 3 Ãsa, diamasi bid̶a mʌ̃a Ãcõrẽa iwid̶ibʌrʌd̶e bʌ carea bia b̶ʌad̶a abaria. Ãcõrẽba jara b̶ʌra crĩcha biad̶eba obaria mʌ̃ drõã naẽnabemarãba oped̶ad̶a quĩrãca.  
\v 4 Mʌ̃ wãbʌrʌ carea bʌra jĩãsia. Maʌ̃ crĩchabʌrʌd̶e acʌd̶e wã quĩrĩã b̶abaria bio b̶ʌsrid̶a b̶ai carea.  
\v 5 Mʌ̃a quĩrãneba b̶abaria bʌa Critora wãrãda ĩjã b̶ʌda bʌ papadjora Loidaba, bʌ papa Eunice bid̶a bʌ naẽna ĩjã panana quĩrãca. Mʌ̃a cawa b̶ʌa bʌa bid̶a ab̶ari quĩrãca Critora ĩjã b̶ʌda.  
\v 6 Mʌ̃ jʌwara bʌ ʌ̃rʌ̃ b̶ʌsid̶e Ãcõrẽba bʌ́a diasia idji itea ne omãrẽã. Maʌ̃ carea mʌ̃a jaraya: Ãcõrẽba diad̶ara biara ẽpẽ odua.  
\v 7 Ãcõrẽba dadjía ne waya b̶ai soda diaẽ́ basía, ãtebʌrʌ dadji sod̶e diasia jũma poya od̶amãrẽã, quĩrĩãda erob̶ead̶amãrẽã, idjab̶a dadji cacuara jipa erob̶ea cawad̶amãrẽã. 
\p  
\v 8 Maʌ̃ bẽrã dadji Boro Jesucritod̶ebemada jarai carea perarãdua. Mʌ̃ra Jesucrito carea preso b̶ʌmĩna perarãdua. Ãtebʌrʌ bed̶ea bia Jesucritod̶ebema jaradiabʌrʌd̶e Ãcõrẽ ʌb̶ʌad̶eba bʌ sid̶a bia mĩgai carea b̶adua.  
\v 9 Ãcõrẽba dadjirãra ẽdrʌ edasia idjab̶a trʌ̃sia idji itea bia b̶ead̶amãrẽã. Dadjia bia o panʌ carea mãwã oẽ́ basía, ãtebʌrʌ idji biad̶eba oida crĩcha b̶ad̶a bẽrã mãwã osia. Wãrãda naʌ̃ ẽjũã b̶ai naẽna Ãcõrẽba idji biad̶eba crĩchasia Jesucritod̶eba dadjirãra carebaida.  
\v 10 Maʌ̃be Jesucrito dadji Ẽdrʌ Edabari zesid̶e unubisia sãwã idji biad̶eba carebabarida. Dadji beuida b̶ad̶ara Jesucritoba jõbiped̶a ewariza zocai b̶aida diasia. Bed̶ea bia idjid̶ebemaba maʌ̃ra ebud̶a cawabi b̶ʌa. 
\p  
\v 11 Ãcõrẽba mʌ̃ra b̶ʌsia maʌ̃ bed̶ea bia jarabarida b̶amãrẽã, Jesucritoba diabued̶ada b̶amãrẽã, idjab̶a judiorãẽ́a jaradiabarida b̶amãrẽã.\f + \fr 1:11 \fq Judiorãẽ́a.\ft  Griego bed̶ead̶e ʌ̃cʌrʌ cartad̶e maʌ̃ra neẽ́a.\f* 
\v 12 Maʌ̃ carea mʌ̃ra bia mĩga b̶ʌa. Baribʌrʌ peraẽ́ b̶ʌa. Mʌ̃a cawa b̶ʌa caida ĩjã b̶ʌda. Idjab̶a cawa b̶ʌa mʌ̃a idji jʌwad̶e wagamãrẽã b̶ʌd̶ada idjia poya wagaida ab̶a idjia cawa oi ewarid̶aa.\f + \fr 1:12 \fq Idji jʌwad̶e wagamãrẽã b̶ʌd̶ada.\ft  Ʌ̃cʌrʌmaarã maʌ̃ bed̶eaba jara b̶ʌa: “Idjia mʌ̃ jʌwad̶e b̶ʌd̶ada.”\f* 
\p  
\v 13 Mʌ̃a jipa jaradia b̶ad̶a quĩrãca jaradia b̶adua. Jesucrito ĩjã b̶ʌd̶eba, quĩrĩãneba nĩbadua.  
\v 14 Ãcõrẽ Jaure dadji sod̶e b̶ʌba wãrã bed̶ea Ãcõrẽba bʌ́a diad̶ara bio waga b̶adua. 
\p  
\v 15 Bʌa cawa b̶ʌa berara jũma djabarã Asia druad̶ebemaba mʌ̃ra igarasid̶ada. Djaba Pigeloba, Hermogene bid̶a mãwã osid̶aa.  
\v 16 Baribʌrʌ mʌ̃a quĩrĩã b̶ʌa dadji Boroba djaba Onesiporo ẽberãrãra quĩrã djuburia b̶aida. Idjia mʌ̃ra b̶arima zocãrã carebasia. Mʌ̃ra carenaba jʌ̃ b̶ʌmĩna mʌ̃ carea quĩrã peraẽ́ basía.  
\v 17 Ãtebʌrʌ Roma purud̶e jũẽped̶a mʌ̃ra quĩrãcuita jʌrʌ nĩne unusia.  
\v 18 Mʌ̃a quĩrĩã b̶ʌa dadji Boroba cawa oi ewarid̶e idjira quĩrã djuburiaida. Bʌa cawa b̶ʌa Onesiporoba Epesod̶e bio carebasida. 
\c 2  
\s1 Sãwã Jesucrito bed̶ea jaradiaida b̶ʌ 
\p  
\v 1 Mʌ̃ warra, Jesucrito biad̶eba zarea b̶adua.  
\v 2 Mʌ̃a zocãrã ẽberãrã quĩrãpita jaradia b̶ad̶ada bʌa ũrĩsia. Ara maʌ̃ jaradia b̶ad̶ara bʌa bid̶a djabarã jipa b̶eaa jaradia b̶adua ãdjirãba ab̶ari quĩrãca dewararãa jaradiad̶amãrẽã. 
\p  
\v 3 Bʌra Jesucrito sordao bia bẽrã mʌ̃ quĩrãca bia mĩgai carea b̶adua.  
\v 4 Sordaoba ne baridua ocaa, ãtebʌrʌ idji boroba quĩrĩã b̶ʌdrʌ obaria bia unumãrẽã.  
\v 5 Idjab̶a dji jemenebarida idji jemeneida b̶ʌ quĩrãca jemeneẽ́bʌrʌ, idjia poyabʌrʌ sid̶a idjia edaida b̶ad̶ara edaẽ́a.  
\v 6 Ẽjũã o b̶ʌra bia mĩgabaria. Maʌ̃ bẽrã idjiabʌrʌ néu zaud̶ad̶ebemada naãrã edaida b̶ʌa.  
\v 7 Mʌ̃a jara b̶ʌra bio crĩchadua. Dadji Boro Jesuba bʌ́a jũma maʌ̃gʌra cawabiya. 
\p  
\v 8 Jesucritod̶ebemada quĩrãnebadua. Idjira David̶eba zed̶aa. Idjira beu b̶ad̶ada Ãcõrẽba ʌ̃rẽbabisia. Maʌ̃ bed̶ea bia idjid̶ebemada mʌ̃a jaradia b̶ʌa.  
\v 9 Maʌ̃ carea mʌ̃ra bia mĩga b̶ʌa. Mʌ̃ra ẽberã cadjirua quĩrãca carenaba jʌ̃ eropanʌa. Baribʌrʌ Ãcõrẽ bed̶eara jʌ̃ eropanʌẽ́a.  
\v 10 Maʌ̃ carea mʌ̃a jũma droa b̶ʌa Ãcõrẽba edad̶a ẽberãrã carebai carea. Mãwã Ãcõrẽba ãdjirã sid̶a Jesucritod̶eba ẽdrʌ edaya ewariza idji bia quirud̶ebemada erob̶ead̶amãrẽã. 
\p  
\v 11 Naʌ̃ bed̶eara wãrã araa: 
\q1 Dadjirãda Crito ume beusid̶abʌrʌ, idji ume zocai panania. 
\q1  
\v 12 Dadjirã bia mĩga panʌda droad̶ibʌrʌ, idji ume dji bororãda b̶ead̶ia. 
\q1 Dadjirãba Critoda adua panʌana ad̶ibʌrʌ, idjia bid̶a dadjirãra adua b̶ʌad̶a aya. 
\q1  
\v 13 Dadjirãda idji ume jipa nĩbad̶aẽ́bʌrʌ, idjida jipa b̶abaria ara idjia jarad̶ara o ama b̶aca bẽrã. 
\s1 Ãcõrẽ nezoca sãwã b̶aida b̶ʌ 
\p  
\v 14 Jũma maʌ̃gʌra djabarãa quĩrãnebabi b̶adua. Dadjirã Boro quĩrãpita jaradua ãdjirãra baridua bed̶ea carea caicaya b̶ead̶iẽ́ panʌda. Maʌ̃ caicayaba biada diacaa, ãtebʌrʌ dji ũrĩ b̶ea crĩchara ãrĩbaria.  
\v 15 Ãcõrẽ wãrã bed̶eara jipa jaradia b̶ʌda unubi b̶adua. Ne obari bia quĩrãca quĩrãcuita o b̶adua Ãcõrẽba bʌra quĩrã pera neẽ́ bia unumãrẽã.  
\v 16 Ãcõrẽ quĩrãpita biẽ́ b̶ea nẽbʌrʌbadara igaradua. Maʌ̃ ẽpẽ b̶eara Ãcõrẽnebemada tʌmʌara wãbadaa.  
\v 17 Ãdjia jaradia panʌba ẽberãrãra ãrĩ wãbaria aid̶aba pea co wãbari quĩrãca. Mãwã jaradiabadarã tãẽna Himeneoda, Pileto sid̶a panʌa.  
\v 18 Ãdjira wãrã bed̶ead̶ebemada ãĩ wãsid̶aa. Ãdjia jaradiabadaa ẽberãrã jaid̶aped̶ad̶ara ʌ̃rẽbacuasid̶ada. Maʌ̃gʌd̶eba ʌ̃cʌrʌba Crito ĩjã panʌra ãdjia ãrĩbʌdaa.  
\v 19 Baribʌrʌ Ãcõrẽ ẽberãrãba Critora bio ĩjã panʌa de jĩrũba dera zarea erob̶abari quĩrãca. Ãcõrẽba idjid̶erãda cawabi carea nãwã jarasia: “Dadjirã Boroba jũma idjid̶erãra cawa b̶ʌa.” Idjab̶a jarasia: “Dadjirã Boro ĩjã panʌana a b̶eaba jũma cadjiruara igarad̶ida panʌa.” 
\p  
\v 20 De waib̶ʌad̶e ab̶abe oro od̶ada, parata od̶a sid̶a b̶eaẽ́a, ãtebʌrʌ bacuru od̶ada, egoro cad̶a sid̶a b̶eaa. Ʌ̃cʌrʌra dji biara b̶ea bẽrã baridua ewari carea b̶eaẽ́a, baribʌrʌ waabemara baridua ewari carea b̶eaa.  
\v 21 Dadjirã sid̶a ara maʌ̃ quĩrãca panʌa. Dadjirãba cadjiruara igarad̶ibʌrʌ, dadjirã Boro itea dji biara b̶eada panania. Mãwã dadjirãneba idjia ne poya oya idjab̶a ne jũma biada od̶i carea b̶ead̶ia. 
\p  
\v 22 Cũdrarãba cadjirua awua panʌnebemada ãĩ b̶adua. Jipa oida ẽpẽ b̶adua. Jesura ĩjã b̶adua. Jũmarãda quĩrĩã b̶adua. Jũmarã ume necai b̶adua. Dadjirã Boro Ãcõrẽa iwid̶ibadarã ume so jipa b̶ʌd̶eba jũma maʌ̃gʌra ẽpẽ b̶adua.  
\v 23 Ẽberãrãba crĩcha siriẽ́ b̶ea bed̶ea panʌne ed̶a bed̶earãdua. Bʌa cawa b̶ʌa maʌ̃gʌd̶eba caicayabadada.  
\v 24 Dadjirã Boro nezocara ijara b̶aiẽ́ b̶ʌa, ãtebʌrʌ jũmarã ume aduá b̶aida b̶ʌa. Jaradia cawa b̶aida b̶ʌa. Jũmarã ume droa b̶aida b̶ʌa.  
\v 25 Idjia jaradia b̶ʌ quĩrĩãnaca ẽberãrãa bed̶ea biad̶eba Ãcõrẽ bed̶eara cawabida b̶ʌa. Mãwãra Ãcõrẽba ãdjirãra carebaisicada idjimaa jẽda zed̶aped̶a wãrã bed̶eada cawad̶amãrẽã.  
\v 26 Quĩrãipa crĩchasid̶ara ãdjirãra diauruba jida erob̶ʌd̶ebemada ẽdrʌd̶ia. Ara nawena diauruba jida pe erob̶ʌa idjia quĩrĩã b̶ʌra od̶amãrẽã. 
\c 3  
\s1 Jĩrũarebema ewarid̶e ẽberãrã sãwã b̶ead̶i 
\p  
\v 1 Bʌa naʌ̃gʌda cawa b̶aida b̶ʌa. Jĩrũarebema ewarid̶e minijĩchiada zeya.  
\v 2 Ẽberãrãba ne jũmada ãdji itea quĩrĩãnia, parata awua b̶ead̶ia, ãdjida biara b̶ead̶a ad̶ia, dji dromada crĩchad̶ia, djãrãda biẽ́ jarad̶ia, ãdji djibarirã bed̶eara ĩjãnaca baya, ãdji carebabʌrʌ ẽberãa bia b̶ʌad̶a ad̶aca baya, idjab̶a Ãcõrẽra wayad̶aca baya.  
\v 3 Ãdjirãba djãrãda quĩrĩãnaca baya, quĩrã djuburiad̶aca baya, nẽbʌra oya b̶ead̶ia, cadjirua od̶ira poya igarad̶aca baya, jʌwaichia b̶ead̶ia, idjab̶a ne jũma biada igarad̶ia.  
\v 4 Ãdji dji bia quĩrãca eropanʌra cũrũga b̶ʌd̶eba biẽ́ od̶ia. Bio crĩchad̶aẽ́ne ne bariduada o b̶ead̶ia. Jũmarã cãyãbara ne cawaara b̶ead̶a ad̶ia. Ãcõrẽ cãyãbara b̶ʌsrid̶ada biara quĩrĩã b̶ead̶ia.  
\v 5 Ãcõrẽ ĩjã b̶eaca b̶ead̶ia baribʌrʌ iduaribid̶aẽ́a Ãcõrẽba idji ʌb̶ʌad̶eba ãdjira jipa b̶ʌmãrẽã. Maʌ̃gʌrã ume ãbaa b̶arãdua. 
\p  
\v 6 Mãwã b̶eara djãrã deza wãbadaa wẽrã crĩcha neẽ́ b̶ea, cadjiruaba bira b̶eada cũrũgad̶i carea. Maʌ̃gʌ wẽrãrãba ne jũma cadjirua o quĩrĩã b̶ʌd̶eba bariduada ĩjãbadaa.  
\v 7 Ãdjirãra ewariza ne cawa wãnaa, baribʌrʌ wãrã bed̶eara poya cawad̶acaa.  
\v 8 Janéba, Jambre bid̶a Moise bed̶ea igaraped̶ad̶a quĩrãca ãĩ jaradia b̶ea bid̶a wãrã bed̶eara igarabadaa.\f + \fr 3:8 \ft  Exodo 7:10-12. Janéra, Jambre sid̶a Egiptod̶ebema ne cawa b̶ea basía.\f* Ãdji crĩchara cadjiruaba jũma ãrĩ b̶eaa. Wãrã bed̶eara cawad̶acaa.  
\v 9 Baribʌrʌ ãdjia o panʌra bia odjaẽ́a. Jũmarãba ãdjira crĩcha neẽ́ b̶eada ebud̶a cawad̶ia Moise ewarid̶e Jané, Jambre mãwãped̶ad̶a quĩrãca.\f + \fr 3:9 \ft  Exodo 8:16-19. Janéba, Jambre bid̶a jũma poya od̶aẽ́ basía Moiseba Ãcõrẽneba od̶a quĩrãca. Mãwã jũmarãba cawasid̶aa ãdjira sewaid̶a b̶eada.\f* 
\s1 Pauloba Timoteoa obid̶a 
\p  
\v 10-11 Baribʌrʌ bʌabʌrʌ jũma mʌ̃a jaradia b̶ʌra bio cawa b̶ʌa. Mʌ̃ nĩbada, mʌ̃a o quĩrĩã b̶ʌda, mʌ̃a Crito ĩjã b̶ʌda, mʌ̃a jũmarã ume droa b̶ʌda, mʌ̃a quĩrĩã erob̶ʌda, mʌ̃ biẽ́ od̶i carea ẽpẽbʌda jũma droa b̶ʌda, mʌ̃ bia mĩga b̶ʌ sid̶a bʌa cawa b̶ʌa. Antioquíad̶e, Iconione, Listrad̶e bid̶a mʌ̃ biẽ́ od̶i carea ẽpẽped̶ad̶ada bʌa bio cawa b̶ʌa.\f + \fr 3:10-11 \ft  Hecho 13:44d̶eba ab̶a 14:21naa.\f* Mʌ̃ra bio bia mĩgasia. Baribʌrʌ dadji Boroba jũma maʌ̃gʌd̶ebemada ẽdrʌ b̶ʌsia.  
\v 12 Wãrãda jũma Jesucrito ĩjã b̶ea Ãcõrẽ quĩrãpita bia nĩnada ẽberãrãba biẽ́ od̶i carea ẽpẽnia.  
\v 13 Baribʌrʌ ẽberã cadjiruarãba, djãrã cũrũgabada bid̶a wetara cadjiruara o wãnia. Djãrãra cũrũga b̶ead̶ia idjab̶a dewararãba ãdjira cũrũgad̶ia. 
\p  
\v 14 Baribʌrʌ bʌa cawad̶ara wãrã arada cawa b̶ʌ bẽrã maʌ̃ra ẽpẽ wãdua. Bʌa cawa b̶ʌa bʌ́a jaradiaped̶ad̶aba jipa jaradiasid̶ada.  
\v 15 Caibe ed̶a Ãcõrẽ Bed̶eara cawasia. Maʌ̃ bed̶eaba bʌ́a cawabi b̶aya ab̶aʌba Critoda ĩjãsira Ãcõrẽba ẽdrʌ edaida.  
\v 16 Ãcõrẽbʌrʌ jũma Idji Bed̶eara b̶ʌbisia. Jũma maʌ̃gʌra bia b̶ʌa jaradiai carea, cadjirua o b̶eara quẽãi carea, ãĩ o b̶eara jipa o cawabi carea, idjab̶a sãwã quĩrãipa nĩbad̶ida cawabi carea.  
\v 17 Mãwã Ãcõrẽ ẽberãrãba ne jũma biada o cawad̶aped̶a poya o panania. 
\c 4  
\p  
\v 1 Jesucritora zeya jũmarã Boroda b̶ai carea. Maʌ̃ne ẽberãrã zocai b̶eara, beuped̶ad̶a sid̶a cawa oya. Maʌ̃ bẽrã Jesucrito quĩrãpita, Ãcõrẽ quĩrãpita bid̶a mʌ̃a naʌ̃ bed̶eada jaraya bʌa omãrẽã.  
\v 2 Ãcõrẽ bed̶eara jaradia b̶adua. Ẽberãrãba ũrĩ quĩrĩã panʌne, ũrĩ quĩrĩãẽ́ panʌne bid̶a jaradiai carea b̶adua. Ãĩ o b̶eara jipa o cawabidua. Cadjirua o b̶eara quẽãdua. Idjab̶a djabarãra carebadua biara ĩjãnamãrẽã. Jũma droa b̶ʌd̶eba, quĩrãcuita jaradia b̶ʌd̶eba mãwã odua.  
\v 3 Ewari ab̶a ẽberãrãba wãrã bed̶eara ũrĩ quĩrĩãẽ́ panania. Ãtebʌrʌ ãdjia quĩrĩã panʌda ẽpẽnia. Maʌ̃ bẽrã jaradiabadada zocãrã jʌrʌd̶ia ãdjia ũrĩ quĩrĩã panʌra jaradiad̶amãrẽã.  
\v 4 Ãdjirãba wãrã bed̶eara ũrĩ ama b̶ead̶ia, maʌ̃ne naʌ̃ dud̶abemaba nẽbʌrʌbadada ẽpẽnia.  
\v 5 Baribʌrʌ bʌra ne jũmane quĩrãipa b̶adua. Bia mĩga b̶ʌd̶e droa b̶adua. Bed̶ea bia Critod̶ebemada jaradia b̶adua. Jũma bʌa Ãcõrẽ itea oida b̶ʌra jipa o b̶adua. 
\p  
\v 6 Dãrãẽ́ne mʌ̃ra bead̶ia.\f + \fr 4:6 \fq Dãrãẽ́ne mʌ̃ra bead̶ia.\ft  Griego bed̶ead̶e nãwã b̶ʌ́ b̶ʌa: “Mʌ̃ra uva b̶a Ãcõrẽa wea diabʌda quĩrãca b̶ʌa.” Maʌ̃ bed̶ead̶eba Pauloba cawabi b̶asia dãrãẽ́ne ẽberãrãba idjira Crito carea bead̶ida.\f* Mʌ̃ beui ewarira caita b̶ʌa.  
\v 7 Mʌ̃a Ãcõrẽ itea oida b̶ad̶ara jũma osia. Jũma jipa osia bia djõna quĩrãca. Mʌ̃a Critora igaraẽ́ b̶ʌa.  
\v 8 Mʌ̃a jipa o b̶ʌ carea dadji Boroba mʌ̃ itea nepeda waga erob̶ʌa. Idjia jipa cawa obari bẽrã maʌ̃ nepera mʌ̃́a diaya idjia cawa obʌrʌd̶e. Baribʌrʌ ab̶abe mʌ̃́a diaẽ́a, ãtebʌrʌ jũma idji zei ewari unu quĩrĩã b̶earãa diaya. 
\s1 Timoteo zemãrẽã Pauloba jarad̶a 
\p  
\v 9 Isabe mʌ̃ acʌd̶e zedua.  
\v 10 Djaba Cresentera Galacia druad̶aa wã b̶ʌa. Titora Dalmacia druad̶aa wã b̶ʌa. Maʌ̃ awara djaba Demába naʌ̃ ẽjũãnebemada biara quĩrĩãna bẽrã mʌ̃ra igaraped̶a Tesalonica purud̶aa wãsia.  
\v 11 Ab̶abe djaba Lucada mʌ̃ ume b̶ʌa. Bʌ zebʌrʌd̶e djaba Marcoda jʌrʌd̶e wãped̶a enedua.\f + \fr 4:11 \fq Marco.\ft  Hecho 13:5; 13:13; 15:36-40.\f* Mʌ̃a Ãcõrẽ itea o b̶ʌra idjia carebaida b̶ʌa.  
\v 12 Djaba Tiquicora mʌ̃a Epesod̶aa wãbisia.  
\v 13 Bʌ zebʌrʌd̶e mʌ̃a jĩsua carea jʌ̃barida enedua. Maʌ̃da Troa purud̶e, djaba Carpo ded̶e b̶esia. Idjab̶a mʌ̃ carta b̶eara enedua. Mʌ̃a biara quĩrĩã b̶ʌa mʌ̃ carta animarã ed̶e b̶ʌ́ b̶eada. 
\p  
\v 14 Jiorrod̶eba ne obari Alejandroba mʌ̃ biẽ́ od̶a carea dadjirã Boroba cawa oya.  
\v 15 Idji ume quĩrãcuita b̶adua. Dadjia jaradia panʌnebemada idjia bio biẽ́ jara b̶ʌa. 
\p  
\v 16 Ara mʌ̃dji carea dji dromarã quĩrãpita bed̶easid̶e ni ab̶aʌda mʌ̃are bed̶ead̶aẽ́ basía. Ãtebʌrʌ jũmarãba mʌ̃ra igarasid̶aa. Mʌ̃a quĩrĩãẽ́a ãdjira maʌ̃ carea Ãcõrẽ quĩrãpita bed̶ead̶e b̶ead̶ida.  
\v 17 Baribʌrʌ dadji Borora mʌ̃ ume b̶asia. Idji ʌb̶ʌada mʌ̃́a diasia idji bed̶ea jaramãrẽã. Mãwã jũma judiorãẽ́ arima duanʌba ũrĩsid̶aa. Maʌ̃ne dadjirã Boroba mʌ̃ra imama ited̶ebemada ẽdrʌ edasia.  
\v 18 Maʌ̃ awara dadjirã Boroba jũma mʌ̃ biẽ́ obʌdad̶ebemada ẽdrʌ edaya. Idjia mʌ̃ra waga edeya idji ẽberãra bajãne bia pe erob̶ʌmaa. Ewariza idjía bio bia bed̶ead̶ida panʌa. Bia b̶ʌa mãwã b̶aida. 
\s1 Pauloba jĩrũare b̶ʌd̶a 
\p  
\v 19 Djaba Aquilaa, Priscaa bid̶a jaradua mʌ̃a quĩrĩã b̶ʌda ãdjira bia pananida. Ara maʌ̃ quĩrãca djaba Onesiporo ẽberãrãa jaradua.  
\v 20 Djaba Erastora Corinto purud̶e b̶esia. Djaba Tropimora cacua biẽ́ b̶ed̶a bẽrã idjira Mileto purud̶e amesia.  
\v 21 Cue jara bai naẽna isabe zedua. Djabarã Eubuloba, Pudenteba, Linoba, Claudiaba, jũma djabarã bid̶a quĩrĩã panʌa bʌra bia b̶aida. 
\p  
\v 22 Mʌ̃a quĩrĩã b̶ʌa dadjirã Boro Jesucritora bʌ ume b̶aida idjab̶a Ãcõrẽba idji biad̶eba bãrãra careba b̶aida. Bia b̶ʌa mãwã b̶aida.\f + \fr 4:22 \fq Bia b̶ʌa mãwã b̶aida.\ft  Griego bed̶ead̶e ʌ̃cʌrʌ cartad̶e maʌ̃ra neẽ́a.\f*